(12, 1, '2018-04-26 12:14:32', '2018-04-26 12:14:32', 'Elizabeth''s heart is broken. For solace, she drops in late at night a few times at Jeremy''s diner for blueberry pie a la mode; they talk. Once, he watchers her sleep, her head on the counter. Abruptly, she leaves New York City to get away from her pain. She works a couple of jobs in Memphis. There, a heart-broken cop is drinking himself into oblivion, his ex occasionally showing up where he drinks and Lizzy works. Then, she''s in Nevada, working at a casino where she uses her savings (she wants a car) to stake Leslie, a busted gambler, in a high rollers'' game. After, Beth drives Leslie to Vegas where Leslie''s estranged father lives. Broken relationships. What about Jeremy?', 'My Blueberry Nights', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'my-blueberry-nights', '', '', '2018-04-26 12:14:32', '2018-04-26 12:14:32', '', 0, 'http://movies:83/?post_type=movies&#038;p=12', 0, 'movies', '', 0),
